DTEND:20060731T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130081@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:While HoH Janelle agonizes over her nominations\, she entertai
 ns "advice" from Chilltown and the floaters. Her final nomination choices 
 promise to shake up the household. In the Food Competition\, several House
 Guests are assigned to a week on the dreaded Slop by their housemates.
END:VEVENT
