DTSTART:20060802T000000Z
DTEND:20060802T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130082@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:The Power of Veto Competition yields a very lucky winner who e
 xercises the Veto to change the nominations. HoH Janelle nominates a float
 er\, and alliances shift again.
END:VEVENT
