SUMMARY:Big Brother - Episode 12
DTSTART:20060804T000000Z
DTEND:20060804T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130083@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:After intense lobbying\, fighting and backstabbing\, one of th
 e floaters is evicted. The HoH Competition kicks off a week of competition
 s requiring the HouseGuests to choose between power and temptation.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Big Brother - Episode 13
DTSTART:20060807T000000Z
DTEND:20060807T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130084@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:Last episode's HoH Competition was a cliffhanger--actually a w
 ebhanger--and Black Widow Danielle manages to cling the longest and win th
 e crown. As she promised\, Danielle gets revenge on the S-6 alliance with 
 her nominations.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Big Brother - Episode 14
DTSTART:20060809T000000Z
DTEND:20060809T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130085@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:With Janelle and James on the block\, the PoV Competition has 
 special significance for S-6\, Chilltown and the Legion of Doom. The compe
 tition offers the players some tough choices\, and one HouseGuest is willi
 ng to risk it all to win. After the Veto Ceremony\, the household is in ch
 aos again\, with the HouseGuests sleeping on cots\, taking cold showers an
 d eating Slop.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Big Brother - Episode 15
DTSTART:20060811T000000Z
DTEND:20060811T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130086@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:Both Kaysar and James want to stay\, but one is ultimately evi
 cted. After a particularly spooky HoH Competition\, a new HoH takes charge
 . Julie Chen announces a new twist that could transform the game: the Coup
  d'Etat.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Big Brother - Episode 16
DTSTART:20060814T000000Z
DTEND:20060814T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130087@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:Technical difficulties force a redo of the HoH Competition\, w
 ith different results. In the Food Competition\, the HouseGuests must impr
 ess a panel of judges from seasons past with a set of Slop-based recipes. 
 The new HoH nominates two floaters.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Big Brother - Episode 17
DTSTART:20060816T000000Z
DTEND:20060816T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130088@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:The PoV Competition brings back events and HouseGuests from se
 asons past. One of Janelle's nominees wins the Power of Veto and saves her
 self. Are Boogie and Erika involved in a showmance?
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Big Brother - Episode 18
DTSTART:20060818T000000Z
DTEND:20060818T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130089@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:In a tearful Eviction Ceremony\, one nominee is shown the door
 . Julie Chen informs Mike Boogie that he's winner of the Coup d'Etat but m
 ust use within the next three weeks. On Prom Night\, a new HoH is installe
 d\, but will reign for only 24 hours and must immediately make nominations
 .
END:VEVENT
