DTSTART:20060821T000000Z
DTEND:20060821T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130090@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:The PoV winner forces short-time HoH George to name a replacem
 ent nominee\, who is swiftly evicted. A special HoH Competition results in
  a first-time win for one All-Star and yet another power shift in the hous
 e.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
