DTSTART:20060823T000000Z
DTEND:20060823T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130091@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:After both nominees play victim\, one wins the PoV\, and HoH B
 oogie swaps in a surprise. While Will secretly resolves to turn her into a
  femme-bot\, Janelle forms a new alliance.
END:VEVENT
