DTSTART:20060828T000000Z
DTEND:20060828T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130093@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:In the Food Competition\, the HouseGuests win a high-protein\,
  high-alcohol diet for the next week\, and George gets a much-needed Slop 
 pass. "Lance Showmance\," aka Boogie\, does his best to work on Erika. HoH
  Erika announces her nominations.
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
