DTSTART:20060830T000000Z
DTEND:20060830T010000Z
DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130094@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:Neil Patrick Harris brings Christmas in August to the BB House
 \, delighting the star-struck HouseGuests. He spends some time in the Diar
 y Room and on Will's trampoline. The PoV Competition is tense\, but one lu
 cky nominee wins it and HoH Erika is forced to swap in another.
END:VEVENT
