DTSTAMP:20260710T141301Z
UID:tvmaze-ep-130098@bigbrother-calendar
DESCRIPTION:The three-part Final HoH Competition yields a winner\, who als
 o wins a fabulous car. The HoH announces the eviction\, and only the Final
  Two remain. Who will win it all?
END:VEVENT
